## Use cases

TODO: In progress

## django-vite-ssr (Node)

This framework delivers the builded apps from Vite into static files that is loaded by `django_vite_ssr`.

See the complete documentation at [Node library documentation](/django-vite-ssr/README.md)

## django_vite_ssr (Python)

This framework loads the delivered apps from `django-vite-ssr` and contextualize them into a server side rendering (SSR) standards, separating `front end` from `back end` responsabilities.

See the complete documentation at [Python library documentation](/django-vite-ssr/README.md)
